{"tid":2439592,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"韓正稱每日都看香港新聞　冀政協助解房屋、經濟等深層次矛盾","createTime":"2021-03-09T11:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T08:51:01.000Z","uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c1e85dcc7bce57a2ffb0d886253cf935b253590b","tid":2439592,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T11:02:39.000Z","msg":"全國人大會議昨日（5日）揭幕，將審議《全國人民代表大會關於完善香港特別行政區選舉制度的決定（草案）》。主管港澳事務的國務院副總理韓正，今早接見約200名港區全國政協委員。<br />\n港區全國政協委員、民建聯彭長緯表示，韓正對香港的事情非常關心，引述韓正指每日早上都會先閱讀香港的新聞，認為在國家領導人心中是非常重視港人。另一港區政協委員、工聯會理事長黃國就指，韓正指出了完善香港選舉制度的必要性和緊迫性，明確完善選舉制度基本原則。"},{"pid":"4feed05075c8784a477be8ad38e67baf4815292e","tid":2439592,"uid":320041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T11:05:07.000Z","msg":"睇文匯定大公<br />\n定why not both<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0545c9b6fe3e94e36da092c2f0da048f7f102b83","tid":2439592,"uid":60177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T11:06:21.000Z","msg":"日日放啲大陸閪落嚟，好想知佢點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd4ac75befcc1feff99619281254614854b8ff9a","tid":2439592,"uid":130079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T11:06:23.000Z","msg":"韓正同黃世澤講野一樣戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n一個睇新聞希望了解房屋政策<br />\n一個就攬住bno講一堆廢話，連用個app都出評論戇撚鳩"},{"pid":"abf0aebdb219ba07c3c86140cc4f28003fa1efc4","tid":2439592,"uid":45708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T11:07:23.000Z","msg":"人地話其中一個深層次問題係醫療，所以叫政府開放中國醫生過嚟，痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81af11f8eff9c5e69bc24b0adf81c86a2a3e14ce","tid":2439592,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T11:07:3